Various AI technologies used in daily news:-
1. Google Maps while we set the destination and we get the shortest route to the destination which is updated on regular basis
2. ChatBots of various companies like Alex from Amazon, Ask Disha from IRCTC, etc.
3. Recommendation Systems : In online shopping sites like Amazon, StarQuick, AJIO, online reading stuffs like Amazon Kindle, Quora, etc, 
                            also OTT platforms like Amazon Prime, Netflix, Disney+ Hotstar, etc.
4. Real time Weather Forecast using IOT
5. Some escalators in Malls, Railway Stations, Airports where they are automatically turned ON/OFF using some kind of sensors and IOT.
6. In automated driving cars like Tesla, wherein real time images of the surroundings around the car is sent over to tesla servers.
